name: Sate Babi Intemanis Rai
address: Q84G+9PF, Jalan Raya, Kintamani, Kec. Kintamani, Kabupaten Bangli, Bali 80652, Indonesia
review 1: Being a tent on the side of the road doesnt really matter when the owner is so kind and cheerful, on top of having some of the most affordable and delicious pork and fish satay on the planet. Rp. 5000 and you get 3 of the stuff, and not just a skinny tiny ones you usually get with cheap satays. Here the meats are thickly cut and well seasoned. Definitely would go back again everytime we visit Bali
review 2: Unbelievable food and friendly staff. Don’t get put off by the fact it’s a tent by the side of the road it’s so good!
review 3: Best satay out there, best sambal, super recommended. This place should have deserves more popularity
